{"tid":844983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做完運動要即刻食野先減到肥！","createTime":"2018-10-02T10:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T07:50:15.000Z","uid":18679,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"309c8f5a75312dc4b6544620fe1d6e42270e24af","tid":844983,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:04:29.000Z","msg":"d肥仔肥妹成日以為做完運動食野咪哂左<br />\n錯！<br />\n因為做完運動隔左兩三個鐘先食野 肚餓感覺會勁左 到時會容易食多左野 同埋食d高熱量野<br />\n<br />\n<em>研究也指出，餓過頭才吃飯、或一點也不餓還進食，恐怕打亂人體代謝機制，醫生表示，餓過頭才吃飯，此時饑餓感需要滿足，很容易吃下比平時還多的食物，尤其是醣類，反而易使胰島素分泌增加，人體血糖一旦失衡，將影響糖化血色素指數，如果一年指數單次大於或等於5.7%，就達糖尿病黃燈警示，罹患第二型糖尿病風險高出一般人3到5倍。</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/315068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F315068&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=48ef5a4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/315068</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>林黑潮解釋，因運動完後血液循環好，馬上進食、營養熱量吸收肌肉有優先權，脂肪較不易堆積，而且消化吸收與食物種類有關，與運動沒有關係，不發胖的前提，一日總熱量必須固定。</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://health.udn.com/health/story/6033/2186386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.udn.com%2Fhealth%2Fstory%2F6033%2F2186386&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=799ad97c\" target=\"_blank\">https://health.udn.com/health/story/6033/2186386</a><br />\n<br />\n咁當然食唔係食m記 kfc呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em>Best Post-Workout Snacks For Weight Loss<br />\nBananas with peanut butter.<br />\nBaked sweet potato and egg.<br />\nGreek yogurt with berries.<br />\nEdamame.<br />\nCottage cheese with vegetable sticks.<br />\nQuinoa salad.<br />\nPost-workout shake.<br />\nSavory muffins.</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.runtastic.com/blog/en/slim-down-with-these-8-post-workout-snacks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.runtastic.com%2Fblog%2Fen%2Fslim-down-with-these-8-post-workout-snacks%2F&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b1c7d030\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.runtastic.com/blog/en/slim-down-with-these-8-post-workout-snacks/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/173912_af11737d31791eca85b03c7403e7bd72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F173912_af11737d31791eca85b03c7403e7bd72.jpg&h=ada2b271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da8345128337e27f91e488444084eece1a775f1","tid":844983,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d026740d368fd4542ff9f9f33002155f7dc411","tid":844983,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba57ce4bfa841e66f1e8047abd409b50c6dc175","tid":844983,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}